channel.title: FFS.. It just won't work!
channel.description:
OKay, well I've got my source, got my no-ip, got my portforwarding done, and it STILL WILL NOT WORK.
I've read the guide under the tut section, a nice and well thought out one, and it helped A LOT. But I still am having problems. I can only loggin to my server using LocalHost, not the IP.
I have no clue what's wrong. I'm thinking it's the no-ip though.. The No-Ip is not connected at all. All i did was make my no-ip, download it, and finished. I think i might be missing somthing connecting the no-ip to the source or somthing..
IDK if that's the reason though, that's just what I thought.
Can anyone help ?
